00:21:19,666 --> 00:21:21,333
so much before you
dissed her club,

484
00:21:21,416 --> 00:21:23,666
but now you've been
working that social link.

485
00:21:23,750 --> 00:21:26,500
If she hates you that bad, why'd
she go on a walk with you?

486
00:21:26,583 --> 00:21:28,416
It was a fluke that
she bumped into me!

487
00:21:28,500 --> 00:21:30,750
She probably only asked
to be polite, y'know?

488
00:21:30,833 --> 00:21:31,583
[TASUKU]
Polite?

489
00:21:31,666 --> 00:21:33,625
Ah, what the hell!

490
00:21:33,708 --> 00:21:35,833
It's odd. They're
my relationships,

491
00:21:35,916 --> 00:21:37,916
but in a way,
you're more invested

492
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:40,750
in my success or
failure than I am.

493
00:21:40,833 --> 00:21:43,291
Well, that's what
friends are for.

494
00:21:43,375 --> 00:21:44,750
You're way too good to me!

495
00:21:44,833 --> 00:21:45,958
I mean that!

496
00:21:46,041 --> 00:21:48,791
[sobs] Thanks for taking
me under your wing!

497
00:21:48,875 --> 00:21:52,166
My life just hasn't been the
same since I met you, Uehara.

498
00:21:52,250 --> 00:21:55,666
How about you save those
lines for the ladies?

499
00:21:57,333 --> 00:21:58,500
[TASUKU, KEITA]
Uh?

500
00:21:58,583 --> 00:22:02,000
Uh, hey guys! You know what?

501
00:22:02,083 --> 00:22:04,500
I have somewhere less
awkward to be! So!

502
00:22:04,583 --> 00:22:10,250
I'm just gonna go there, and...
I swear I didn't see anything!

503
00:22:10,333 --> 00:22:11,500
[TASUKU, KEITA]
Mm?

504
00:22:11,583 --> 00:22:12,875
[TASUKU]
Hm?

505
00:22:12,958 --> 00:22:16,666
Aw, FML! Meet-up's
cancelled. See ya later!

506
00:22:16,750 --> 00:22:18,458
Hey, come back!
It's not what it looks like!

507
00:22:18,541 --> 00:22:21,875
We were just talkin'
about dude stuff!

508
00:22:21,958 --> 00:22:24,250
What?! Wait,
why'd they run away?

509
00:22:24,333 --> 00:22:26,458
I need to call Aguri
on the double!

510
00:22:26,541 --> 00:22:30,666
This sucks! I don't
get any of this!

